                        <interp inst="t18400511-name-963" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN M'LLELE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am footman to a lady in Wimpole-street, I was going along Lisson-grove on the 10th of May—I stopped to bear a man delivering lectures on temperance—I felt something tug at my pocket—I turned and collared the prisoner with my handkerchief in his hand—this is it—(<hi rend="italic">examining one</hi>)—it had been in my pocket.</p>
